name: XX8 - E.T. "ADAHN"
description:
January 3, 2032
Jimra said he knew an alien civilization located near a star called “Copernicus”. The Moxxapha had contact with them long time ago, and these aliens are “Adahn” with their homeworld “55 Cancri e”. “55 Cancri e” was a super earth discovered back then in 2004, also known as “Janssen”

We immediately went there as directed by Jimra, and unfortunately this planet has already crushed to the ground. We went to search for any survivors as many as we can, we found couple of survivors and evacuated them to our vessel. When we asked what happened, they told us they were attacked by an unknown aliens without any warning and we conclude that was an attack from the alien invader.

The “Adahn” have white glowing pair of eyes, they stand at around 5 inches, greyish skin  with black accent around their body, they speak really loud somehow with a growl, and a really unique shaped head. Because of their glowing eyes, I nicknamed them “Lighthouse”.

Another victim of the alien invader, we really need to act fast about this whole situation, this is inevitable. We need to prepare for the worst, the whole civilization rely on this alliance.

Brig Gen. Abraham C. Easley
January 6, 2032
